OL,3,CIllegal disposable vapes still being
OL,4,Csold - ITV News investigation
OL,6,FThey might be banned, but just how
OL,7,Feasy is it to get hold of a disposable
OL,8,Fvape?
OL,10,FA ban on single-use disposable vapes
OL,11,Fwas brought in during the summer aimed
OL,12,Fat protecting children's health and
OL,13,Fthe environment.
OL,15,FBut we've found that many of the now
OL,16,Fillegal vapes were still being sold -
OL,17,Fwith authorities seemingly powerless
OL,18,Fto stop them.
OL,20,FOur secret cameras filmed the purchase
OL,21,Fof disposable vapes in Brighton.
