OL,6,FVapes that it's been illegal to sell
OL,7,Fsince June - but sold freely here. And
OL,8,Fthis despite the visits of Trading
OL,9,FStandards Inspectors. We then took our
OL,10,Ffindings to the local council.
OL,12,F'A lot of the time deterrents aren't
OL,13,Fworking' - Cllr David McGregor, from
OL,14,FBrighton and Hove City Council
OL,16,FIt's thought there are around 100
OL,17,Fdifferent shops selling vapes in
OL,18,FBrighton and Hove.
