OL,6,FOn a single day we visited 25 of which
OL,7,Fwe found seven still selling the
OL,8,Fillegal disposable versions - that's
OL,9,F28 per cent committing crimes.
OL,11,FAll these exchanges that Brighton
OL,12,FCouncil believes could be the tip of
OL,13,Fthe iceberg in the sale of illicit
OL,14,Fgoods. It says it's seized 11,500
OL,15,Fvapes since the ban was introduced.
OL,17,F'It should be a level playing field' -
OL,18,FJoey Dowsing, Red Eye Vape Store
