OL,6,FMeanwhile, experts believe alternative
OL,7,Fmodels, that look exactly like the
OL,8,Fdisposables they replaced, are just as
OL,9,Fregularly being thrown away.
OL,11,FVapes contain lithium batteries and
OL,12,Fhave been labelled 'bombs in bins' due
OL,13,Fto the fires they cause.
OL,15,FThe ban was brought in to stop them
OL,16,Fbeing binned unnecessarily, protecting
OL,17,Fthe environment and making them less
OL,18,Fattractive to children.
