OL,6,FSchools in the city have been working
OL,7,Ftogether over the past two years to
OL,8,Freduce take-up, but say their concerns
OL,9,Fover packaging remain.
OL,11,F'Manufacturers are targeting young
OL,12,Fpeople' - Donna Marie Janson,
OL,13,FPrincipal, Varndean College
OL,15,FCEO if the Independent British Vape
OL,16,FTrade Association, Gillian Golden,
OL,17,Ftold us: "We understand the
OL,18,Ffrustrations and concerns for the
OL,19,Fsafety of waste facility staff due to
OL,20,Fimproperly discarded vape waste.
