OL,6,F"Since the single use vapes ban came
OL,7,Finto force in June, our member's sales
OL,8,Fof reusable and rechargeable products
OL,9,Fhas been very encouraging.
OL,11,F"It points to more consumers
OL,12,Frecharging and refilling devices
OL,13,Frather than just throwing them away
OL,14,Fafter one use. Less battery waste is
OL,15,Fcertainly now being generated in the
OL,16,Flegitimate sector.
