OL,6,F"It is very important for consumers to
OL,7,Funderstand that throwing vapes away in
OL,8,Fgeneral waste is environmentally
OL,9,Funfriendly, as well as being a fire
OL,10,Frisk.
OL,12,F"Vape disposal should now be available
OL,13,Fin all places that sell vapes and is
OL,14,Fmost certainly available in all good
OL,15,Fvape shops. It allows vapes to be
OL,16,Fdisposed of safely and for recoverable
OL,17,Fmaterials to be properly recycled."
